{"tid":1436931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭話反政府者無經濟貢獻 但實情係越低收入越撐林鄭","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:30:42.000Z","uid":19552,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5412d62845ca4a2c2c3ac8ba19a2812284d580","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"研究所又分析受訪者背景，發現「51歲或以上」及「小學或以下程度」的受訪者較其他組別傾向支持支持林鄭月娥當特首。另外「男性」、「30歲或以下」及「大專或以上程度」就較其他組別更傾向不支持林鄭當行政長官。<br />\n<br />\n是次調查研究所成功訪問了736名18歲或以上的市民，成功回應率是39.8%，以736個成功樣本推算，百分比變項的抽樣誤差約為正負3.61%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭支持者係低收入 低學歷 高齡一族，簡稱廢老"},{"pid":"9990a13ab426c45cf2d389f1d273b73555393050","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94aa9b7fb3e3e442622afbdb5905a0bd64929d5","tid":1436931,"uid":135461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e1f0398c78c531c128b1266aa9463cfe2cd565","tid":1436931,"uid":135096,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"支持政府有以下呢幾種人<br />\n1.低學歷 低技術勞工 對社會無咩經濟貢獻<br />\n2.新移民 無貢獻不特止 仲要拎綜援拎資助<br />\n3.真廢老 退哂休嘅維園呀伯 又係拎生果金唔貢獻<br />\n大家知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2003bf2399238bd6f05221bccb39c2fdf7dd2f37","tid":1436931,"uid":5649,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"「男性」、「30歲或以下」及「大專或以上程度」<br />\n<br />\n一眾巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4758d5f19b469916d3aaeb815b4563142b412631","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雖然林鄭民望大幅落後，但相對而言她在50 歲或以上、預科或以下學歷、沒有收入和低收入等範疇上，普遍獲得比較多的民意支持。</span><br />\n<br />\nvs曾俊華"},{"pid":"a51ffb2e0c8f35f0fda58c3c77b4b2015eea067e","tid":1436931,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"「51歲或以上」及「小學或以下程度」= 習近平"},{"pid":"11bda628957b2411338ba6e5a4b8ae0c16940fc6","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班綜援廢老成世人最自豪事件係鬧大學生 納稅人做廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5526a0803a19ac3795c0f756b9735f4723a24b5","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e76be82cd4ca279ed84a1d0dd851f278f2061d7","tid":1436931,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"[經濟戰] 中共林鄭最怕香港信貸評級下跌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436815</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba5aeb40f378684e0a4d7c3ba102f370e72fdbbf","tid":1436931,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b040d32437af5aa21966b59ae0c6a7c1165591c5","tid":1436931,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded5676a24ac47db458d8afd5308fbcfba025876","tid":1436931,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"樓主係有錢的廢老 五張野仲扮後生"},{"pid":"23a2b536577d2e482e6a6daa3ee9163992fba972","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ded5676a24ac47db458d8afd5308fbcfba025876","tid":1436931,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"樓主係有錢的廢老 五張野仲扮後生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"我碩士生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c08c0595434d64c8cddf0c4e8e5e5c6219edee","tid":1436931,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"俾北京條廢物村恐嚇番d 廢老就岩<br />\n仲有少少勞動力就係會俾新移民取代"},{"pid":"29891ba425c18c0d9cbd4c05168f80b18c622701","tid":1436931,"uid":281912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"示威帶動工程用品收入"},{"pid":"a82fecc2574a090b2c36f64e335430f336b2860a","tid":1436931,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11bda628957b2411338ba6e5a4b8ae0c16940fc6","tid":1436931,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班綜援廢老成世人最自豪事件係鬧大學生 納稅人做廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人有文化又有料過佢地"},{"pid":"2e4b13b327e6d5ff7962eb2ae90d0927daff7656","tid":1436931,"uid":36592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"林鄭評分breakdown:<br />\n30 歲或以下（20.0 分）vs 51 歲或以上（32.1 分）<br />\n小學或以下（39.3 分） vs 和大專或以上（20.1 分）<br />\n中下層 （28.2 分） vs 中層 （25.0 分）<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkiaps.cuhk.edu.hk/wd/ni/20190806-143119_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkiaps.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fwd%2Fni%2F20190806-143119_1.pdf&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=0834b536\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkiaps.cuhk.edu.hk/wd/ni/20190806-143119_1.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c4d7c83a1d5d9336431dbda8c02cc74c6c22f31b","tid":1436931,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"推到林奠睇到紅都面哂<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫權、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"37ec055a738def1b62e3df987b8185a647bc2f61","tid":1436931,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51ffb2e0c8f35f0fda58c3c77b4b2015eea067e","tid":1436931,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"「51歲或以上」及「小學或以下程度」= 習近平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc752dc3bc9ada01eff41f7030f082235a9c6cc","tid":1436931,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cf0726122f50de00ced38252debd17c24b86d7","tid":1436931,"uid":135891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得罪反開佢嘅人好過得罪撑開佢嘅人<br />\n佢咁係為咗比廢老支持者打飛機同令佢地抗拒我地嘅文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好輕敵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsTudG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsTudG0.jpg&h=22b16974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TcVTG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7T